com.camerontec.catalys.server.ha.collections.message

Class ReplayResponseMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.ha.collections.message.DistributedCollectionMessage
      • com.camerontec.catalys.server.ha.collections.message.ReplayResponseMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExternalizableData, Cloneable

    public final class ReplayResponseMessage
extends DistributedCollectionMessage
implements Cloneable
    Class representing a replay response message.

    A replay response message is sent from a distributed collection to the requesting peer on another node in response to a ReplayRequestMessage.
